import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react' import "./Checkout.css" import { useParams } from 'react-router-dom' import { useSelector } from 'react-redux' const Checkout = () => { const [product, setProduct] = useState() const [exist, setExist] = useState() const productId = useParams().productId const cartItems = useSelector(state => state.cart.items) const fetchProduct = async () => { setExist(prev => cartItems.find(item => String(item.id) === String(productId.id))) console.log("Exist", exist) if (exist) { setProduct(exist) } else { const response = await fetch(`https://fakestoreapi.com/products/${productId}`) const data = await response.json() setProduct(data) } } useEffect(() => { fetchProduct() }, [productId]) console.log("Checkout", product) return (
